Subject: Unable to start nginx webserver
Description:
After adding a valid license via the gui and restarting the system, on startup the message is displayed "[FAILED] Failed to start A high performance web server and reverse proxy server".
The server continues the startup however the website is not reachable
What_We_Know__c:
- Client reporting  that he is unable to start nginx webserver 
- Sent client email requesting availability for joining a remote session or when would he would be available to join a remote session
Solution_Comment__c: Moved the setup.nginx.conf from the initial location and the UI could be started after that.
